<p><strong>标题：</strong>SCP-2990-JP - ────, that is the question.<br />
<strong>原文：</strong> <a href="http://scp-jp.wikidot.com/scp-2990-jp">http://scp-jp.wikidot.com/scp-2990-jp</a><br />
